Output json.gif
Set Theme "Catppuccin Mocha"
Set FontSize 14
Set Width 1000
Set Height 400
Set Padding 15
Set Margin 8
Set Framerate 10
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.9

Type "pi --mode json -p --provider kimi-coding --model kimi-k2.6 'write a bash script to check disk usage and alert if above 90%'"
Enter
Sleep 10s
Sleep 2s
